{"tid":618584,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗被爆曾因倒掛被救出 發脾氣怒啤對方門將","createTime":"2018-04-06T02:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T22:43:06.000Z","uid":54373,"like":56,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f208232b07d013346c31b23d4ec52c6414eab8a9","tid":618584,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:32:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">掛幾十球先難得踢中次,緊係嬲嬲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0406 03:00<br />\n<br />\n皇家馬德里球星基斯坦奴朗拿度在周二歐聯射入一球倒掛金勾，成為了整個球壇的焦點。不過曾經效力格蘭納達的門將羅拔圖就踢爆C朗小器的一面。<br />\n<br />\n格蘭納達2014年曾經在西甲作客皇馬，羅拔圖更在該仗救出過C朗的倒掛攻門，近日他接受訪問時就憶述了當日球場外的情況：「我在球員通道內看到C朗十分忿奴，因為他一直想用倒掛金勾取得入球，可是那場比賽他沒有成功，我還記得卡斯拿斯賽後更走過來稱讚我的撲救。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，談論到C朗今次的驚世入球，羅拔圖亦同意把關的保方絕對無法救出這個射球，但他認為最大功勞要歸於負責傳中的丹尼爾卡華積。"},{"pid":"0dd975e8b430e5ffd9cb4b849b314d424819eff7","tid":618584,"uid":36372,"like":27,"dislike":13,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"樓主走先 我頂住"},{"pid":"37115bc9dd3183c61accb40bbfcc07d1d0500f31","tid":618584,"uid":69064,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0dd975e8b430e5ffd9cb4b849b314d424819eff7","tid":618584,"uid":36372,"like":27,"dislike":13,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"樓主走先 我頂住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:34:25.000Z","msg":"我地頂住"},{"pid":"47ca8cba17e9ebc50465db7c41b1218925907304","tid":618584,"uid":90515,"like":14,"dislike":7,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:35:11.000Z","msg":"樓主唔怕被狗咬"},{"pid":"ab514f4ac60ccb3918a9bed58b3c83ecf599e511","tid":618584,"uid":19552,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:36:04.000Z","msg":"樓主返來了"},{"pid":"0db0a0df318055ce3b0c498d1177ffe3fc92f04f","tid":618584,"uid":18384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:3